description:
Josh and Heather visit Ireland’s Spike Island, a former prison, to investigate reports of paranormal activity. They explore the island’s cells and tunnels looking for evidence of ghosts. Tune in to new episodes of #ExpeditionX, Wednesdays at 9P on Discovery.

Stream Full Episodes of Expedition X:

#Discovery #ExpeditionX

About Expedition X:
Explorer Josh Gates has put together a team to undertake investigations delving into realms beyond the "unknown." Jessica Chobot and Phil Torres join his quest to mount unprecedented expeditions into the unexplained and perhaps unexplainable.
